org.jhove2.module.aggrefy
Class AggrefierModule

java.lang.Object
  org.jhove2.core.reportable.AbstractReportable
      org.jhove2.module.AbstractModule
          org.jhove2.module.aggrefy.AggrefierModule
All Implemented Interfaces:
Reportable, Aggrefier, Module
@Persistent
public class AggrefierModule
extends AbstractModule
implements Aggrefier

JHOVE2 aggregate identifier module. Identifies presumptive instances of Clump formats (e.g. ShapeFiles) in an aggregate Source, and performs callback to JHOVE2 framework to characterize those Clump format instances

Author:
smorrissey
